message: Hi Bob, I suggest a 60-40 split in my favor. This is a fair offer considering we both need to reach an agreement, and you'll get your money immediately without any inflation impact.

Hi Alice, I appreciate your offer, but I believe a 50-50 split would be more fair for both of us. This way, we both get an equal share of $5000, and we can conclude this quickly before any inflation effects come into play.
